cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with the analysis of metadata in social media platforms, specifically Twitter, and the identification of users through machine learning algorithms. This falls under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of obfuscation strategies, which could also be categorized under Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The use of machine learning algorithms for classification also falls under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
